                            <comment id="15288045" author="becket_qin" created="Wed, 18 May 2016 01:28:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=gwenshap&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;gwenshap&quot;&gt;gwenshap&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ijuma&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ijuma&quot;&gt;ijuma&lt;/a&gt; I just submitted PR. The current patch is using 0.10.0-IV0. Please let me know if you reach agreement on changing it to 0.10.0.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
